Yes, Strides has implemented projects to reduce Green House Gas emission specifically carbon footprint
reduction. They are as follows:
Installed 1,470 KW solar power plants and harvested clean energy from roof top solar power panels;
Sustaining solar power consumption by importing solar power from third party and In-house generation;
51.6% of the total power consumption in all sites are from renewable sources (Solar & wind)

Awareness Training/session/module;
Water Consumption Monitoring;
Awareness/ Caution boards display;
Installation of flow meters;
Installation of Piezometer at required sites
